2813315251", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031649_1170182816648584_7761015419150064044_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ORYFZiIxgHQQ7kNvgFhg_WG&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBZPQ1KyI0JJhpx4uW9szj9sw85aqACcqkwrpRhDJTCMA&oe=66CC8159"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CoverImageLandscape_horiz_white_center_(9cw).png", "id": "2797780667125725", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031434_2797780670459058_121874044104596879_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PZXP26cbMPMQ7kNvgGKU2Lp&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCOtoJf9QhQumFq7P7MHvlyvs0eiWsoPMkqiSQ6pXHw4g&oe=66CC57D3"}, "display_name": "Alcove", "keywords": ["family", "travel", "health", "social", "relax"], "long_description": "A portal to new worlds, a virtual home filled with endless experiences to discover and explore, a place to connect with loved ones. World travel, casual games, media customization, adventure, and relaxation.\n\n- Invite your friends and family, and travel together to new places to see the world - hundreds of virtual travels to all continents: take a city tour, a hot air balloon ride, a back-country road trip\n- Explore the depth of the ocean - go diving in the Great Barrier Reef of Australia, or swim with dolphins in the Pacific Ocean\n- Relax and practice meditation in nature - guided, or unguided\n- Listen to classical music\n- Play with your virtual pet\n- Play games, share photos, upload and watch your own videos - standard, and 360, and step into them together.\n\nAlcove has something for everyone, no matter your age. Download Alcove and start exploring today!", "short_description": "A portal to new worlds, a virtual home filled with endless experiences to discover and explore, a place to connect with friends and family. World travel, casual games, media customization, adventure, and relaxation."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.ren